Normalization
it is used to make units same.
Type of Normalization: 

1. MINMAX SCALING :

   formula -- xi=(xi-min)/max
   class -- MinMaxScaler 
   when used -- when you see too much difference between two features
   
   
   
2. Mean Normalization :

   formula =(Xi-xmean)/(Xmax-Xmin)
   class = No 
   used when -- numeric data given and centered data given
   
   
   
 3. MaxAbsScaling :
 
   formula =Xi/|Xmax|
   class = MaxAbsScaler
   when_used =spared data ,when lots of zero
   
   
 4. Robust Scaling :
   formula = (Xi-Xmedian)/IQR              IQR=75%-25%
   when used = when there is outlier
 
 

   
 
Is feature Scaling Required ?
--yes
----Standardization or Normalization?
------- Standardization --mostly
------- Normalization --if you know the value of minimum and maximum will be in this particular range then use MINMAX SCALING ,example --CNN(computer neural network).
